===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*deyḱ-}}
{{lbor|en|ML.|dictiōnārium}}, from {{der|en|la|dictiōnārius}}, from {{m|la|dictiō||speaking}}, from {{m|la|dictus}}, perfect past participle of {{m|la|dīcō|t=speak}} + {{m|la|-ārium|t=room, place}}. {{surf|en|diction|-ary}}.

