==Czech==

===Etymology===
[[každý]]

===Pronunciation===
* {{cs-IPA}}
* {{rhymes|cs|ɪtʃkiː|s=3}}

===Pronoun===
{{cs-pron}}

# {{diminutive of|cs|každý|POS=pronoun}}: every single
#: {{syn|cs|každinký}}

====Usage note====
* The word has adjectival inflection. It is ranked as a pronoun following SSJC. The semantic modification follows that of diminutive adjectives, that of intensification: thus, ''uzoučký'' means very narrow while ''každičký'' means every single or every without exception, intensifying or amplifying ''každý'' (every).

===Further reading===
* {{R:PSJC}}
* {{R:SSJC}}

