==English==

===Etymology 1===
From {{inh|en|enm|of}}, from {{inh|en|ang|of||from, out of}}, an unstressed form of {{m|ang|af}}, {{m|ang|æf||from, off, away}}, from {{inh|en|gmw-pro|*ab}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*ab|t=away; away from}}. {{doublet|en|off}}, which is the stressed descendant of the same Old English word. More at {{l|en|off}}.

