* {{l-lite|en|shoulda}}
* {{l-lite|en|woulda}}

===Etymology 5===
From {{inh-lite|en|enm|a}}, a reduced form of {{m-lite|enm|he||he}}/{{m-lite|enm|ha||he}}, {{m-lite|enm|heo||she}}/{{m-lite|enm|ha||she}} and {{m-lite|enm|ha||it}} (as well as of {{m-lite|enm|hie|hie, hie|they}}).

====Alternative forms====
* {{l-lite|en|'a}}

====Pronunciation====
* {{a|RP}} {{IPA-lite|en|/ə/}}
* {{sense-lite|it}} {{a|RP}} {{IPA-lite|en|/ə/|/ɑ/}}
* {{rhymes-lite|en|ə|ɑ|s=1}}

====Pronoun====
