==Albanian==

===Etymology 1===
* According to Orel, the particle and conjunction are etymologically identical. From {{inh|sq|sqj-pro|*a}} and cognate to {{cog-lite|grc|ἦ|tr=ê|t=indeed|sc=polytonic}}.<ref>{{R:sq:Orel|'''a''' part. ('whether'), conj. ('or')|page=1}}</ref>

* From {{inh|sq|sqj-pro|*(h)au}}, from {{der|sq|ine-pro|*h₂eu-|t=that}}. Cognate to {{cog-lite|grc|αὖ|tr=aû|t=on the other hand, again|sc=polytonic}}. A proclitic disjunctive particle, used with one or more parts of the sentence.

====Pronunciation====
* {{IPA-lite|sq|/a/}}

====Conjunction====
{{head-lite|sq|conjunctions|langname=Albanian}}

# [[or]]
# [[there]]

===Etymology 2===
From {{inh|sq|sqj-pro|*(h)an}}, from {{inh|sq|ine-pro|*h₂en|t=there}}. Cognate with {{cog-lite|la|an|t=yes, perhaps}}. Interrogative particle, usually used proclitically in simple sentences.

====Pronunciation====
* {{IPA-lite|sq|/a/}}

====Particle====
{{head-lite|sq|particles|langname=Albanian}}

# [[probably]], [[perhaps]]
# [[whether]]

====Letter====
{{head-lite|sq|letters|lower case||upper case|A|langname=Albanian}}

# {{ng-lite|The first letter of the Standard [[Albanian]] Latin-script alphabet.}}

===See also===
* {{list:Latin script letters/sq/simple}}
