==Haitian Creole==

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA-lite|ht|/a/}}

===Article===
{{head-lite|ht|articles|langname=Haitian Creole}}

# [[the]], ''[[definite article]]''

====Usage notes====
This term only follows words that end with an [[oral]] (non-[[nasal]]) [[consonant]] and an oral [[vowel]] in that order, and can only modify [[singular]] nouns.

====See also====
* {{l-lite|ht|an}}
* {{l-lite|ht|la}}
* {{l-lite|ht|lan}}
* {{l-lite|ht|nan}}
* {{l-lite|ht|yo}}
* {{l-lite|ht|yon}}

