==Hungarian==

===Etymology 1===
See {{m-lite|hu|az}}.

====Pronunciation====
* {{IPA-lite|hu|[ˈɒ]}}
* {{audio|hu|Hu-a.ogg|Audio}}
* {{rhymes-lite|hu|ɒ|s=1}}

====Article====
{{head-lite|hu|articles|definite|langname=Hungarian}}

# [[the]]
#: {{ux-lite|inline=1|hu|'''a''' hölgy|'''the''' lady}}
# {{lb|hu|before some time phrases}} [[this]]
#: {{ux-lite|inline=1|hu|'''a''' héten|(during) '''this''' week}}

=====Usage notes=====
Used before words starting with a consonant.

=====Related terms=====
* {{l-lite|hu|az}} {{q-lite|for words starting with a vowel sound}}

====Pronoun====
{{head-lite|hu|pronouns|demonstrative|langname=Hungarian}}

# {{lb|hu|in reduplicated constructions formed with postpositions}} [[that]]
#: {{ux-lite|inline=1|hu|'''A''' mellett a ház mellett vártam rá.|I waited for him/her next to '''that''' house.}}

====Determiner====
{{head-lite|hu|determiners|demonstrative|langname=Hungarian}}

# {{lb|hu|rare|only in consonant-initial fixed phrases|with zero article}} {{alt form-lite|hu|az|id=that-determ-zeroarticle||that}}.
#: {{uxi|hu|Foglalja össze, miről szóltak az '''a''' heti beszédek és leckék.|Summarize what '''that''' week’s sermons and lessons were about.|ref=<ref>[http://www.e-nyelv.hu/2011-10-20/a-heti/ a heti] at ''e-nyelv.hu''</ref>}}
#: {{ux-lite|inline=1|hu|November 12-én, az '''a''' havi frissítőkedden jelenhet meg.|It may be released on November 12th, on the Patch Tuesday of '''that''' month.}}
#: {{uxi|hu|Kérjük szíves tájékoztatásukat '''a''' tekintetben, hogy…|We kindly request your information in '''that''' &#91;&#61;&nbsp;the&#93; aspect…|q=&#61;&nbsp;''ab'''ban&nbsp;a''' tekintetben'', see [[az#Determiner|az]]}}
#: {{ux-lite|inline=1|hu|[[amondó|'''a'''mondó]] vagyok, hogy…|I am of the opinion that…, what/all I can / want to say is that…|lit=I am '''that'''-sayer/-saying…}}

===Etymology 2===

====Pronunciation====
* {{sense-lite|letter or phoneme itself}} {{IPA-lite|hu|[ˈɒː]}}<ref>{{R:SiptarTorkenczy 2007}}, p. 280</ref>
* {{sense-lite|identifier or musical note}} {{IPA-lite|hu|[ˈaː]}} {{q-lite|in the names of minor scales; see also {{m-lite|hu|A}}}}

====Letter====
{{head-lite|hu|letters|lower case||upper case|A|langname=Hungarian}}

# {{senseid|hu|letter}} ''The first [[letter]] of the Hungarian [[alphabet]], written in the [[Appendix:Latin script|Latin script]].''
# {{lb|hu|music}} {{ng-lite|designation of the sixth note from C and the corresponding tone}}

=====Derived terms=====
* [[a-moll]]

===See also===
* {{list:Latin script letters/hu/simple}}

