* {{audio|nb|NB - Pronunciation of Norwegian Bokmål «a (fransk)».ogg|Audio}}
* Hyphenation: {{lang-lite|nb|a}} <!-- {{hyphenation|nb|a}} -->
* {{homophones|nb|A|à|A-|a-|ah}}

