===Etymology 1===
From {{uder|pt|la|a}}<!--, form of {{m-lite|la|A}}, from {{der|pt|ett|𐌀}}, from {{der|pt|grc|Α||alpha}}, from {{der|pt|phn|𐤀|t=aleph}}, from {{der|pt|egy|𓃾}}-->.

