| align="center" | {{l-self-lite|scn|na}}
|}

===Etymology 3===
From the lenition of {{m-lite|scn|la}}, from the apheresis of {{inh|scn|VL.||*illa}}, from {{inh-lite|scn|la|illam}}, from {{m-lite|la|illa}}.

====Alternative forms====
* {{l-lite|scn|la}} {{q-lite|liquid form}}

====Pronunciation====
* {{IPA-lite|scn|/a/}}

====Pronoun====
{{head-lite|scn|pronouns|g=f-s|plural|i|masculine|u|langname=Sicilian}}

# {{lb|scn|accusative}} [[her]]
#: {{ux-lite|inline=1|scn|'''A''' canusci?|Do you know '''her'''?}}
#: {{syn-lite|scn|la}}
# {{lb|scn|accusative}} [[it]], [[this]] or [[that]] thing
#: {{syn-lite|scn|la}}
#: {{ux-lite|inline=1|scn|Quannu '''tâ''' desi.|When I gave '''it''' to you.}}

=====Usage notes=====
* This pronoun can blend in contracted forms with other particles, especially other personal pronominal particles.

