# ''Used at the end of a sentence for confirmation, similarly to'' 'didn't I' ''in English.''
#: {{ux-lite|sl|Tega nisi pričakoval, '''a'''?| You did not expect this, '''did you'''?}}

=====Synonyms=====
* {{l-lite|sl|ah|langname=Slovene}}
* {{l-lite|sl|e|langname=Slovene}}
* {{l-lite|sl|eh|langname=Slovene}}
* {{l-lite|sl|o|langname=Slovene}}
* {{l-lite|sl|oh|langname=Slovene}}
* {{l-lite|sl|uh|langname=Slovene}}

===Etymology 3===
From {{inh|sl|sla-pro|*a}}, from {{inh|sl|ine-pro|*ō̃t}}, which is [[ablative]] form of {{inh|sl|ine-pro|*e-}} 'this'. Cognates with {{cog-lite|sh|a}}, {{cog-lite|ru|а|tr=a|sc=Cyrl}} and {{cog-lite|cs|a}}.

====Pronunciation====
* {{IPA-lite|sl|/a/}} <!--{{sl-IPA|a}}-->

