==Swahili==

===Particle===
{{head-lite|sw|particles|head=-a|langname=Swahili}}

# The [[genitive]] [[particle]]; [[adjectival]] particle; [[of]]

====Usage notes====
* This particle agrees in class with the noun preceding it.
* When used as an adjectival particle, the particle itself is untranslated:
** {{ux-lite|inline=1|sw|[[nguo]] '''za''' [[kufuliwa]]|[[laundry]], [[washing]]|lit=[[laundry]] [[clothing]]}}
** {{ux-lite|inline=1|sw|[[mali]] '''ya''' [[pamoja]]|[[communal]] [[property]]}}
* When used as a genitive particle, the particle is sometimes untranslated:
** {{ux-lite|inline=1|sw|[[bahari|Bahari]] '''ya''' [[Hindi]]|[[Indian Ocean]]}}

====Inflection====
{{sw-decl-verbal|a}}

====See also====
* {{l-lite|sw|enye|-enye}}: the [[ornative]] [[particle]]

