From {{inherited|en|enm|to|t=to}}, from {{inherited|en|ang|tō|t=to}}, from {{inherited|en|gem-pro|*tō}}, {{m|gem-pro|*ta||to}}, from {{inherited|en|ine-pro|*de}}, {{m|ine-pro|*do||to}}. Cognate with {{cog|sco|tae}}, {{m|sco|to||to}}, {{cog|frr|to}}, {{m|frr|tö}}, {{m|frr|tu||to}}, {{cog|stq|tou||to}}, {{cog|nds|to||to}}, {{cog|nl|toe||to}}, {{cog|de|zu||to}}, {{cog|fy|ta||to}}. Non-Germanic cognates include {{cog|sq|ndaj||towards}}, Irish {{m|ga|do||to, for}}, Breton {{m|br|da||to, for}}, Welsh {{m|cy|i||to, for}}, {{cog|ru|до||to}}. {{doublet|en|too}}.

===Pronunciation===
