==Old English==

===Etymology===
From {{inh|ang|gem-pro|*tō}}, {{m|gem-pro|*ta||to}}, from {{der|ang|ine-pro|*de}}, {{m|ine-pro|*do||to}}. Cognate with {{cog|osx|tō||to}}, {{cog|goh|zuo||to}}, {{cog|sga|do}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{ang-IPA|tō}}

===Preposition===
{{ang-prep|head=tō}}

# [[to#English|to]], [[into]]
# [[at]]
# {{lb|ang|grammar}} used to mark the infinitive (supine) of the verb
#: {{uxi|ang|'''tō''' drīfenne|'''to''' drive}}
# [[as]]
