==Irish==

===Preposition===
{{ga-prep|d|e}}

# {{alternative form of|ga|i}}

====Usage notes====
This variant of {{m|ga|i}} is used before vowel-initial words, before {{m|ga|bhur||your {{g|p}}}}, before {{m|ga|dhá||two}}, before titles of books, films, and the like, and before foreign words that resist mutation.

In older texts, the ''n'' is spelled together with a vowel-initial word (e.g. {{m|ga|i n-aice le}} instead of modern {{m|ga|in aice le||beside}} and {{m|ga|[[i]] [[nÉirinn]]}} or {{m|ga|[[i]] [[n-Éirinn]]}} instead of modern {{m|ga|in [[Éirinn]]||in Ireland}}. Also in older texts, {{m|ga|in [[bhur]]}} may be spelled {{m|ga|[[i]] [[nbhur]]}}.

