==Lombard==

===Alternative forms===
* {{l|lmo|ind}} (''followed by article'')
* {{l|lmo|en}}, {{l|lmo|èn}} (''Eastern orthographies'')

===Etymology===
From {{der|lmo|la|in}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA-lite|lmo|/in/|/iŋ/}} (''Western'')
