[[Image:Burde guest house.jpg|thumb|In khet.]]

===Etymology===
From {{inh|zom|tbq-kuk-pro|*ʔim}}, from {{inh|zom|sit-pro|*k-jim ~ k-jum|*kim|house, womb}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA-lite|zom|/ǐn/}}

===Noun===
{{zom-noun|ín}}

# [[house]]

====Derived terms====
{{col4|zom
|inva}}

===References===
* {{R:zom:Singh:2013|page=41}}
* {{R:zom:Tungdim:2014}}

