|passage="I'm sure we'll get a '''make''' on the suspect's prints by day break, so if you come down town, I'll see you get everything available. Go ahead and process the car, we won't have any need of it."}}
#* {{quote-book|en|year=2007|author=P. T. Deutermann|title=Hunting Season: A Novel|publisher=St. Martin's Press|isbn=9781429903585
