#: {{ux|en|I'm '''getting''' hungry; how about you?}}
#: {{ux|en|I'm going out to '''get''' drunk.}}
#* '''November 1, 1833''', {{w|Samuel Taylor Coleridge}}, ''Table Talk''
#*: His chariot wheels '''get''' hot by driving fast.
