|title=[http://openlibrary.org/works/OL5535161W Mr. Pratt's Patients]
|page=175|pageurl=https://archive.org/details/cu31924021760941/page/n188/mode/1up|passage=Afore we got to the shanty Colonel Applegate stuck his head out of the door. His temper had been '''getting''' raggeder all the time, and the sousing he got when he fell overboard had just about ripped what was left of it to ravellings.}}
# {{lb|en|transitive}} To [[cause]] to become; to bring about.
#: {{ux|en|That song '''gets''' me so depressed every time I hear it.}}
#: {{ux|en|I'll '''get''' this finished by lunchtime.}}
