#: {{ux|en|We ought to '''get''' moving or we'll be late.}}
#: {{ux|en|After lunch we '''got''' chatting.}}
#: {{ux|en|I'm '''getting''' to like him better now.}}
# {{lb|en|transitive}} To [[take]] or [[catch]] (a scheduled transportation service).
#: {{ux|en|I normally '''get''' the 7:45 train.}}
#: {{ux|en|I'll '''get''' the 9 a.m. [flight] to Boston.}}
