#: {{ux|en|Can you '''get''' that call, please? I'm busy.}}
# {{lb|en|intransitive|followed by infinitive}} To be [[able]], be [[permitted]], or have the opportunity (to do something desirable or ironically implied to be desirable).
#: {{ux|en|I'm so jealous that you '''got''' to see them perform live!}}
