#: {{ux|en|Yeah, I '''get''' it, it's just not funny.}}
#: {{ux|en|I don't '''get''' what you mean by "fun". This place sucks!}}
#: {{ux|en|I mentioned that I was feeling sad, so she mailed me a box of chocolates. She '''gets''' me.}}
# {{lb|en|transitive|informal}} To be [[tell|told]]; be the [[recipient]] of (a question, comparison, opinion, etc.).
