#: {{uxi|sv|Jag vill '''be om''' en tjänst|I want to '''ask''' you a favor}}
#: {{uxi|sv|Han '''bad''' honom lämna rummet|He '''asked''' him to leave the room}}
# to [[pray]]
#: {{uxi|sv|De satt i kyrkan och '''bad'''|They sat in church, '''praying'''}}
# to [[beg]], to plead with someone for help or for a favor
#: {{uxi|sv|Hjälp mig! Jag '''ber''' dig!|Help me! I '''beg''' of you!}}

